The paper deals with the problem of detecting botnets, which is a major issue in computer security (cs.CR). The authors use machine learning algorithms and graph-based representations of data, which are techniques commonly used in network security and data analysis (cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.DS). The paper also presents a novel approach for identifying data generated by botnet activity, which could be of interest to researchers in machine learning and data mining (cs.LG).
